  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Prior Information Group Properties Pane</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Prior Information Group Properties </text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">pane is on the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Pest_Properties_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">PEST Properties Dialog Box</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> under </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Prior Information</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The variables specified on the </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Prior Information Group Properties</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> pane are described in the PEST User Manual, Part I, Section 4.10). More extensive descriptions of these variables are in the PEST user manual. The variables specified on this pane appear in the Observation Groups section of the PEST control file.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><snippet src="PestObsGroupProperties"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Usually prior information is used for regularization. Clicking the button at the top of the pane will check all the check boxes in the </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Regularization Group</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> column.</text></para>
  </body>
